  "text": "Co-immunoprecipitation (co-IP) was performed as previously described. Briefly, Whole cell extracts of Flag-SLC2A4RG and Myc-14-3-3θ co-transfected Hek293T cells were prepared in the presence of protease inhibitors cocktail (Sigma-Aldrich). Immunoprecipitation of Flag-SLC2A4RG was conducted by adding 10 μl of anti-Flag M2 affinity sepharose (Sigma) and incubated overnight at 4°C. Finally, the immunecomplex was detected by Western blot. The GST-pulldown assay was conducted as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
